### MVP PLAN ###
MVP target: introduce safe, parameterized action metadata and dry-run validators before any write/merge/release automation.
- Add action spec model for GitHub PR check/merge, release verify, DOI record, finalize state.
- First commands should be read-only or dry-run by default.
- Mutating variants require explicit execute flag and machine-readable preconditions.
- No raw chat terminal blocks for routine PR/release actions after MVP.
- GUI later consumes these action specs rather than shell snippets.

